7587
05:00:28.220 --> 05:00:29.500
En aquel arroyo

7588
05:00:29.979 --> 05:00:31.340
bebimos todos.

7589
05:00:32.699 --> 05:00:33.659
qué delirio,

7590
05:00:34.575 --> 05:00:36.255
qué incomparable

7591
05:00:36.255 --> 05:00:37.295
voluptuosidad,

7592
05:00:38.415 --> 05:00:40.255
qué era aquella agua,

7593
05:00:40.575 --> 05:00:41.855
