10713
07:02:48.923 --> 07:02:49.563
dientes.

10714
07:02:49.883 --> 07:02:51.403
El Plesiosauro,

10715
07:02:51.403 --> 07:02:53.803
serpiente de tronco cilíndrico,

10716
07:02:53.963 --> 07:02:56.363
